EDITOR APPROVED

You are wondering what is this 'Editor Approved'?

Well, this is pretty awesome! In order for the post to qualify and receive this accolade, it has to have a minimum of 700 words and two images (at least one original).

Receiving this accolade means two things: 1) Your content is amazing! Good job! 2) Your content qualifies for our monetization program. Every week two of the most read posts receive monetary rewards.

Thanksgiving Outfit Inspiration

Product details:

2 189 views
  • by Erica Sullivan 8 followers
FOLLOW WHATTHECLIQUE

    Wow, how crazy is it that Thanksgiving is less than a week away? It seems like the fall has really flown by. Matt and I are packing to leave Blacksburg Sunday morning, so I’m finally starting to think about what I want to wear on Thanksgiving; preferably something with a little stretch! I’m sharing some of my favorite looks for Thanksgiving below.  

    CASUAL + CLASSY 

    You can never go wrong with jeans and a black t-shirt. Dress the look up with a pair of loafers or booties.
